        {"test": "Platelets - paediatric (all ages)", "value": "150 - 400 x10^9/L", "units": "x10^9/L"}
      ],
      "notes": "Physiological nadir at 2 - 3 months (term) reflects switch from HbF to HbA and falling EPO. Lymphocyte predominance from 1 week until approximately age 5. RCH Clinical Practice Guidelines / RCPA paediatric intervals."
